---
title: Plant-Based Herby Sausages & Potato Mash with Caramelised Onion Gravy & Steamed Greens
description: It's bangers and mash with a difference! Our herby sausages are plant based and packed with homestyle herby
flavours. We've topped them with a sweet, yet tangy caramelised onion gravy, then paired it with a Calorie Smart potato and a sprinkle of chives.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/plant-based-herby-sausages-potato-mash-59135c47.jpg
